Text:
Simple Installation:
1] Install The App
2] Disconnect From Internet
3] Enter Serial(Activation Error Comes Ignore It)
4] Now See That you are a Pro User
5] Don't Refresh Your License otherwise You Have To Repeat This Process
6] Enjoy This Release!!
Cheers

* Clean your registry.(Old keys may create problem)
* Install and enter the key while you are offline.
* Then, try to use firewall or hosts file edit.
